description: This course covers the material in Mathematics 126 in greater depth and breadth. Prerequisite: 4 or 5 on AP Calculus AB exam or permission of the Mathematics Placement Director. Credit may be earned for either Mathematics 126 or 128, but not both. Offered annually in the fall semester.
